Kellie Bright https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kellie_Bright 0 Kellie Denise Bright (born 1 July 1976) is an English actress. Her roles include Linda Carter in the BBC soap opera EastEnders, for which she won the 2015 British Soap Awards for Best Actress and Best Dramatic Performance, Julie in Ali G Indahouse, Joanna Burrows in The Upper Hand (1990–96), Cassie Tyler in Bad Girls (2002) and Joan Trotter in Rock Chips (2010–11). In 2015, she was the runner-up in the 13th series of the BBC One show Strictly Come Dancing. Kellie_Denise_Bright ( born 1_July_1976 ) is an_English_actress .
